                             Management Seminar
                                 (MIT-300D)
                              STRESS MANAGEMENT
                          With Don Hudson (Adjunct)
                         Wednesday, October 31, 2001
                            Pacific: 9 AM - 11 AM
                          Mountain: 10 AM - 12 noon
                            Central: 11 AM - 1 PM
                           Eastern: 12 noon - 2 PM

   Method of delivery: 2-hour* Interactive Television (ITV) broadcast

   Duration: 4-hour*

   To Register:
   To register for this course, please contact your site training point of
   contact. If you do not know who your site point of contact, please call
   Customer Service at (505) 845-5170 X310.

   Please register now.

     * The final deadline for registering is Friday, October 12, 2001.

                               Prerequisites:
                                    NONE

                           Questions on Content?:
      E-mail Dr. J. H. Olsen, Jr., Lead Instructor: jolsen@nnsi.doe.gov

                                 *Logistics:
              One 10-minute break; OK to bring a snack or lunch

   Who can Participate?
   This two-hour seminar is designed for all management, professionals,
   staff, clerical and supervisory personnel. The satellite broadcast is
   free to DOE personnel and contractors, and is available to participants
   from other government agencies for a nominal fee.

   For other federal agencies: $138.58 per participant.

   To register for this course, please contact your site training point of
   contact. If you do not know who your site point of contact is, please
   call Customer Service at (505) 845-5170 X310. (Note: If you have
   colleagues at another agency, who may not receive this notice, call
   Angela Chavez in Registration and we'll get information to them.)

   What content will these presentations cover

     * Definition of "Stress"
     * Physical Affects and Stress Dynamics
     * Causes of Stress
     * Tools for Dealing with Stress

   Who are the presenters?
   Dr. Jim Olsen Jr. -Moderator, NNSI/Central Training Academy
   Don Hudson of Hudson Enterprises (Adjunct)






